{"tid":2258251,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"馬祖南竿遭中國抽砂船包圍 海巡署急派2000噸級巡防艦前往驅離","createTime":"2020-10-26T01:30:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T04:41:45.000Z","uid":292499,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7d026bcf81067c544c904b2d6f8e95830d14181b","tid":2258251,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T01:30:11.000Z","msg":"有馬祖南竿當地民眾今天披露，今日一早南竿海面出現大批中共漁船，仿若圍島。海巡艦隊分署今天表示，今天越界陸船多是運砂船，艦隊分署緊急調派新北艦全速趕往南竿海域，支援馬祖海巡隊強勢取締越界陸船，也感謝熱心民眾提供相關資訊。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n艦隊分署緊急調派新北艦全速趕往南竿海域，支援馬祖海巡隊強勢取締越界陸船。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/10930/4962957?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F10930%2F4962957%3Ffrom%3Dudn-catelistnews_ch2&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oANVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=290e6f16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/10930/4962957?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/10930/4962922\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F10930%2F4962922&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oANVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=67966241\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/10930/4962922</a>"},{"pid":"f411d4deaf528ba7ce1481dca499afe601e5bb2f","tid":2258251,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T01:30:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c45865ca466746b9d4bc218dfee743e070da941","tid":2258251,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T01:30:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=